data.description: Located in Greystone Estates nestled into a friendly cul de sac this home has desired craftsman elevation an oversized backyard with established professionally treated turf. This house plan has a starting price of over $330,000. Why wait up to one year when you can move into this lovely home next month? LVP flooring, quartz countertops, and upgraded lighting enhance the aesthetic of this split floor plan home. The unfinished basement has an egress window and is located near the bathroom rough-in to accommodate your future guest room. The large roof has been well utilized when dozens of solar panels were installed on the South facing back half Sept 2022. Stated by the seller this 14kW system nets a monthly electric bill of $10 per month for current family of three. As the solar loan is nontransferable this new warrantied system is rolled into the price of this nearly new home. For those who are VA eligible, you may assume the remaining VA loan of approximately $218,000 at 2.5%.
